Naruto, Sasuke, and Sakura summon [[Gamakichi]], [[Aoda]], and [[Katsuyu]], respectively. Katsuyu jumps into the air and slams down on the opponent, Aoda then attacks from underground and pushes the opponent up in the air where Gamakichi slashes the opponent with his sword. Naruto, Sasuke and Sakura then jump from their respective summon's head, and land a punch on their opponent, Naruto with a tailed beast chakra arm, Sasuke with a partially manifested Susanoo, and Sakura with her chakra enhanced strength.
